== Version 2.0.0

* Renamed STR2CSTR to StringValuePtr
* Converted to new 1.9.2 char style by calling .ord where appropriate

== Version 1.0.1

* Fixed a bug in the brighten command.

== Version 1.0.0

* Added DRb support (x10/cm17a_remote)

* Added a DRb server (x10server.rb)

* Removed queries from the X10 device API.  Since the
  device object can't report the _actual_ state of the X10 device,
  allowing queries for the state seems misleading.

== Version 0.9.0

Initial release.
